Package com.example.ctrlaltelite

Class MoodEvent

java.lang.Object
com.example.ctrlaltelite.MoodEvent
public class MoodEvent extends Object
Represents a mood event recorded by a user. Stores details like emotional state, reason, trigger, social situation, timestamp, location, and an optional image.
